Cook bacon in skillet until crisp. Remove bacon and drain, reserving 2 tablespoons bacon drippings. Cook onion and peppers in bacon drippings until tender. Add BUSH'S BEST Blackeye Peas and hot sauce and heat through. Prepare cornbread mix using 9 x 13-inch pan. Cook according to directions. Cut into 2-inch squares. Top with blackeye peas, salsa, sour cream and crumbled bacon.